{"title":"The Ultimate Setup Collection","description":"\u003cp\u003eUpgrade your room from plain to powerful with The Ultimate Setup Collection. Designed for bedrooms, gaming corners, study spaces, work desks, and fan rooms, this collection brings together ready-made wall setup packs that instantly add personality to your space.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNo need to search and select designs one by one. Each pack is curated to create a bold, stylish, and complete setup look with minimum effort.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","products":[{"product_id":"ultimate-fan-wall-setup-a4-pack","title":"Ultimate Fan Wall Setup - 24 A4 Pack","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"product-description\"\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eUltimate Fan Wall Setup - A4 Pack\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTurn your plain wall into a bold, stylish fan-inspired setup with this ready-made A4 wall decor pack. Designed for bedrooms, gaming corners, study rooms, work desks, and personal spaces, this pack gives your wall an instant aesthetic upgrade without the confusion of choosing designs one by one.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis collection brings together a strong mix of action, music, racing, cinematic, and pop-culture-inspired visuals to create a powerful collage-style wall setup. Just arrange them like the reference image, stick them neatly, and your room gets a complete makeover.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eWhy You’ll Love It\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eComplete ready-to-decorate wall setup\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePerfect for fan rooms, gaming setups, study spaces, and bedroom walls\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCurated mix of bold, stylish, and high-impact visuals\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEasy to arrange as a collage wall\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClean matte finish for a premium look\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGreat option for anyone who wants an instant room upgrade\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eProduct Details\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003ePack Type:\u003c\/strong\u003e Curated wall setup pack\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSize:\u003c\/strong\u003e A4 only\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003ePrice:\u003c\/strong\u003e ₹549\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eFinish:\u003c\/strong\u003e Matte finish\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eUsage:\u003c\/strong\u003e Bedroom wall, gaming setup, study room, workspace, dorm room, or creative corner\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eWhat’s Included?\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYou will receive the complete A4 wall setup pack as shown in the product images. The designs are selected to match the overall collage look, so you can recreate a similar wall setup easily.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eHow to Use\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eChoose the wall or corner you want to decorate.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePlan the layout before sticking.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse glue dots, double-sided tape, or any wall-safe adhesive.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStick the prints neatly with equal spacing for the best look.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEnjoy your upgraded wall setup.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ol\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eImportant Note\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThese are printed sheets and are not self-adhesive. Adhesive, tape, glue dots, frames, and other accessories are not included unless mentioned separately. The final look may slightly vary depending on wall color, lighting, spacing, and arrangement.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eBest For\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFans who want a bold room setup\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGaming and desk setup decoration\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBedroom wall makeover\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStudents and hostel rooms\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGift for friends who love stylish wall decor\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52031760400680,"sku":null,"price":549.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/UltimateFanWallSetup-A4Pack_2.jpg?v=1782366819"},{"product_id":"m416-legendary-weapon-split-panel-set-gaming-wall-combo","title":"M416 Legendary 3 Weapon Skin | Split Panel Set | Gaming Wall Combo","description":"\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \u003ch2\u003eM416 Legendary Split Wall Combo\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\n  \u003cp\u003e\n    Bring a bold gaming-room look to your wall with this 11-piece M416-inspired split poster combo. The set includes one large Glacier design in 13×19\" and two A3 split designs featuring Fool and Crimson Skyblade themes.\n  \u003c\/p\u003e\n\n  \u003ch3\u003eDesign Highlights\u003c\/h3\u003e\n  \u003cp\u003e\n    The Glacier design creates a frozen blue centerpiece with icy textures, crystal effects, and bold “DOMINANCE” typography. The Fool design adds a dark purple chaos theme with neon accents, while the Crimson Skyblade design brings fiery orange energy with flames, embers, and dramatic weapon detailing.\n  \u003c\/p\u003e\n\n  \u003ch3\u003eWhat's Included\u003c\/h3\u003e\n  \u003cul\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e1 × M416 Glacier 5-Piece Split Set – 13×19\"\u003c\/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e1 × M416 Fool 3-Piece Split Set – A3\u003c\/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e1 × M416 Crimson Skyblade 3-Piece Split Set – A3\u003c\/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTotal: 11 Poster Panels\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n  \u003cp\u003e\n    A complete wall combo made to give your bedroom, gaming setup, or PC corner a premium weapon-skin inspired look.\n  \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52040449065256,"sku":null,"price":599.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/WallMock_f7283275-3f5d-46f9-98f4-8d19f949f88f.jpg?v=1782726943"},{"product_id":"car-enthusiast-poster-pack-split-panel-set","title":"22 Piece Automotive Wall Setup Combo (1 Split Set + 21 A5 Print)","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTurn your wall into the ultimate automotive showcase.\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe \u003cstrong\u003eAutomotive Wall Setup Combo\u003c\/strong\u003e is designed for true car enthusiasts who want more than just a single poster. Featuring one bold \u003cstrong\u003e13×19 Split Poster\u003c\/strong\u003e as the centerpiece and \u003cstrong\u003e21 premium A5 automotive posters\u003c\/strong\u003e, this collection transforms any room into a modern garage-inspired display.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eFrom legendary supercars and JDM icons to luxury performance machines and timeless classics, every design has been carefully selected to create a premium, balanced wall arrangement. Whether it's your bedroom, gaming setup, workstation, studio, or garage, this combo delivers an eye-catching automotive aesthetic instantly.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eEach poster is printed in high resolution on premium matte paper with vibrant colors, deep blacks, and crisp details to ensure every design stands out beautifully. The centerpiece split poster creates a bold focal point, while the surrounding A5 posters complete the gallery wall with a clean, professional finish.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e📦 What's Included\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e1 × 13×19 Split Poster (3-Piece Set)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e21 × A5 Premium Posters\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTotal: \u003cstrong\u003e22 Posters\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePremium Matte Finish\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHigh-Resolution Print Quality\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFrame Not Included\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e✨ Why You'll Love It\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eComplete ready-to-install automotive gallery wall.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFeatures iconic performance, JDM, luxury, and supercar designs.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCreates a premium showroom-inspired room aesthetic.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSharp colors with rich contrast and premium matte finish.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePerfect centerpiece for gaming setups, workstations, garages, bedrooms, and studios.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExcellent gift for every car enthusiast.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e📐 Product Specifications\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eCenterpiece:\u003c\/strong\u003e 13×19 Split Poster (3 Pieces)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSurrounding Posters:\u003c\/strong\u003e 21 × A5 Posters\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eTotal Pieces:\u003c\/strong\u003e 22\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eMaterial:\u003c\/strong\u003e Premium Matte Paper\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003ePrint:\u003c\/strong\u003e High-Definition Digital Printing\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eFrame:\u003c\/strong\u003e Not Included\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e🏠 Ideal For\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGaming Rooms\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBedroom Wall Decor\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCar Enthusiast Setups\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGarage \u0026amp; Workshop Decoration\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOffice \u0026amp; Workspace Decoration\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eContent Creator Backgrounds\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePrice:\u003c\/strong\u003e ₹499\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e*Colors may vary slightly due to monitor settings and photography lighting. Posters are supplied unframed and are intended to be mounted using poster tape, glue dots, or frames.\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52042944250152,"sku":null,"price":499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/AutomativeSet-up.jpg?v=1782821666"}],"url":"https:\/\/www.posterized.in\/collections\/the-ultimate-setup-collection.oembed","provider":"Posterized","version":"1.0","type":"link"}